# ARSession.CollaborationData.Priority.optional

**Case**

A priority that indicates that collaboration can continue without this data.

## Declaration

```swift
case optional
```

## Discussion

ARKit sets the data [doc://com.apple.arkit/documentation/ARKit/ARSession/CollaborationData/priority-swift.property] to [doc://com.apple.arkit/documentation/ARKit/ARSession/CollaborationData/Priority-swift.enum/optional] when the data is important and time-sensitive but the session can continue if it’s not received.
